<L>__{exterior gotham park night}
<A>__{fires burn in garbage cans. tents and lean tos dot the snowy landscape. men, women, and children wander aimlessly, huddling against the cold. an army of the homeless has set up camp in gotham park. on the nearby periphery, picketers half concerned citizens, half down and outers are marching the sidewalks, keeping a candlelight vigil. hand lettered placards read: "save the park." "parks are for people." "this park is our home." the source of the protest? a towering sign posted in a corner of the park, announcing the imminent consuuction of a new luxury highrise the gotham park towers a project of shaw construction, inc. a lamborghini sits at a traffic light nearby...}
